name: Light as our shield
description:
We dance through the storm,
with light as our shield. 
Revealing our shadows, 
We dance until ​they're healed. 
 
We dance through the world, 
shine light on despair, 
the ugly, the flawed
the shadows in our air. 
We dance for you to see, 
that someone out there cares. 
With our light as our shield, 
we dance because we care.
